To Kill the PID using CMD 
C:\>echo off & (for /f "tokens=5" %a in ('netstat -aon ^| findstr 4723') do Task
kill /PID "%a" /F) & echo on
Just save as .bat file the Port PID will kill
FOR /F "usebackq tokens=5" %%i IN (`netstat -aon ^| find "<port>"`) DO taskkill /F /PID %%i
